name: ch.i4ds.organicawild
description:
Organica Wild as a Package

Generate beautiful organic and natural feeling terrain with this Unity Package.
To. Get started faster by importing some of the samples.

samples.description: Contains Samples for how to use the Cellular Automata Interface
Contains Samples for how to use the Poisson Disk Sampling Interface
Contains Samples for how to use the Pipeline Interface
Contains Samples for how to use the Graph Grammar and Shape Grammar Interface
Contains Samples Assets that also need to be imported to use other samples
Contains Samples for how to use the Evolutionary Algorithm Interface
